{"word":"G2151 - εὐσεβέω - eusebéō - yoo-seb-eh'-o - Show piety","slug":"G2151","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐσεβέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>eusebéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yoo-seb-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Show piety"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03C3;&#x03B5;&#x03B2;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - eusebeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>yoo-seb-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2152\">G2152</a>; to <i>be pious</i>, that is, (towards God) to <i>worship</i>, or (towards parents) to <i>respect</i> (<i>support</i>): - show piety, worship."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2150\">G2150</a>, <a href=\"#/G2152\">G2152</a>, <a href=\"#/G2153\">G2153</a>, <a href=\"#/G4573\">G4573</a>, <a href=\"#/G4574\">G4574</a>, <a href=\"#/G4575\">G4575</a>, <a href=\"#/G4576\">G4576</a>, <a href=\"#/G763\">G763</a>, <a href=\"#/G764\">G764</a>, <a href=\"#/G765\">G765</a>"}]}